(7, 1, '2016-07-11 14:23:08', '2016-07-11 14:23:08', '[vc_row full_width="stretch_row" full_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1469429041479{background: #ffffff url(http://localhost:8084/johnMainaSite/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2.jpg?id=39) !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1469429147617{background-color: #0086d8 !important;}"][orane_welcome_banner title="eBiz Technologies" details="We make it simple for you to run your business with increased productivity. As your business grows, we bring in technology that makes it very easy to monitor and manage your business.\r\nThe solution we give you is easy to adopt and doesn''t require any special training to use it." image="90"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_services][orane_single_service title="Monitoring and supervision systems" details="We create software system that enables you to run all your businesses easily any time any place. You can easily do this using a mobile phone, a computer or a tablet. The system is light and very easy to use. Anyone can use it!"][orane_single_service title="Inventory systems" details="We create inventory systems that helps you to track your stock all the time. Just from your phone, you can know how much stock you need to add, which item is moving faster, and much more"][orane_single_service title="Sacco Systems" details="Our sacco systems are unique such that we have automated most of sacco operations, leaving the staff with much less to do. This is because over time, we have learnt that small saccos don''t have dedicated staff working in the office, hence a need to reduce the work load. "][orane_single_service title="E-commerce and corporate Websites" details="Sell anything online. We create for you a an attractive ecommerce websites where customers can easily purchase items using a computer, tablet or mobile phone"][orane_single_service title="Mobile apps" details="Mobile apps are a great way to keep your customers close to you. We create mobile apps for new systems or to be integrated with your current system."][orane_single_service title="Digital Marketting" details="Let your adverts feature in social media and most popular mobile apps. This helps you to target a particular group, timing and much more."][/orane_services][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_vc_gtstarted_banner title="GROW YOUR |BUSINESS|" link_title="Read More" link="url:%23asd|title:ASD|"]Let us handle the complexity, and concentrate on expanding your business. Keep grow; we keep it under control. Becuase we are trained and experienced to do that. [/orane_vc_gtstarted_banner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_vc_projects_portfolio title="Our |Featured| Work"]We have made it possible for many businesses to grow huge while managing them remains easy. Our technologies are very easy to integrate and to operate, hence even people who didn''t have any knowledge of computers are happily using our technology. A few of the businesses below[/orane_vc_projects_portfolio][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_vc_banner_side_image title="Kings Way |sacco|"]We found them with over 200 members, and managing the savings, loans etc was becoming a nightmare. They felt a too big group to manage. We saved them! Now they feel like a very small group that''s just starting up! They are increasing day and day out, but the management isn''t feeling the pressure.[/orane_vc_banner_side_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content" content_placement="middle"][vc_column][orane_vc_features_bgimage title="Rams Investments can now manage all their businesses from one place, in real-time" feature1l="Managers at each small businesses feeds basic data to the system" icon1l="youtube-square" feature2l="The system computes all important parameters, and updates the central database" icon2l="youtube-square" feature3l="Advises the managers on issues like which stock to add" icon3l="youtube-square" feature4l="Limits what managers can see if there is something confidetial." icon4l="youtube-square" feature1r="The owner can see data from all the businesses on one screen" icon1r="youtube-square" feature2r="Important summary on individual businesses and a general summary on all businesses" icon2r="youtube-square" feature3r="Maintaining books of accounts " icon3r="youtube-square" feature4r="Sending alerts and important emails " icon4r="youtube-square" subtitle="Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur." image="95"]Rams Investment is have several small business in Eastlands. Created for them a system that intgrates all the small businesses so that they can all be viewed, monitored and controlled from one place.[/orane_vc_features_bgimage][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" gap="10" equal_height="yes"][vc_column][orane_vc_features_big_image title="Sarcem |Real-Estate |" feature1="Search for a house or a land quick enough" feature2="Look for rentals conveniently- clear images" feature3="Ask for services like conveyance, valuation, construction etc." feature4="Connect with real estate agents " link_title="Visit Real Estate Website" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fsarcemholding.co.ke%2F|title:Sarcem%20Real%20Estate%20Website|" image="63"]Sarcem holding ltd now has a great website which has turned out a great tool for their real estate business.[/orane_vc_features_big_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_vc_features_small_image title="Cahawa |E-commerce| website" image="98"]Cahawa investment ltd is now growing so fast after we exposed them to the world. Customers all over the country now purchase items from their online shop, and pay via mobile money, online banking or card services. [/orane_vc_features_small_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_vc_features_bgimage title="Wynton House of Music Management system and Portal" feature1l="Admit music students" icon1l="youtube-square" feature2l="Match tutors and available rooms to students" icon2l="youtube-square" feature3l="Create Lessons schedule" icon3l="youtube-square" feature4l="Update the schedule as the parameters change" icon4l="youtube-square" feature1r="Every tutor and student can view schedules relevant to them" icon1r="youtube-square" feature2r="Apply for rescheduling" icon2r="youtube-square" feature3r="Accounting module" icon3r="youtube-square" feature4r="Generate reports and alerts" icon4r="youtube-square" image="95"]Wynton school of music is now digitalised, management simplified, and above all, smooth flow of information between the school and their students, and across all departments.[/orane_vc_features_bgimage][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" type="container"][vc_column][vc_text_separator title="" border_width="3"][vc_gmaps link="#E-8_" title="Located at Mamlaka road, Nairobi Kenya"][contact-form-7 id="4" title="Contact Us"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2016-07-26 13:53:54', '2016-07-26 13:53:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/johnMainaSite/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
