nagers can see if there is something confidetial." icon4l="youtube-square" feature1r="The owner can see data from all the businesses on one screen" icon1r="youtube-square" feature2r="Important summary on individual businesses and a general summary on all businesses" icon2r="youtube-square" feature3r="Maintaining books of accounts " icon3r="youtube-square" feature4r="Sending alerts and important emails " icon4r="youtube-square" subtitle="Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur." image="95"]Rams Investment is have several small business in Eastlands. Created for them a system that intgrates all the small businesses so that they can all be viewed, monitored and controlled from one place.[/orane_vc_features_bgimage][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" gap="10" equal_height="yes"][vc_column][orane_vc_features_big_image title="Sarcem |Real-Estate |" feature1="Search for a house or a land quick enough" feature2="Look for rentals conveniently- clear images" feature3="Ask for services like conveyance, valuation, construction etc." feature4="Connect with real estate agents " link_title="Visit Real Estate Website" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fsarcemholding.co.ke%2F|title:Sarcem%20Real%20Estate%20Website|" image="63"]Sarcem holding ltd now has a great website which has turned out a great tool for their real estate business.[/orane_vc_features_big_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_vc_features_small_image title="Cahawa |E-commerce| website" image="98"]Cahawa investment ltd is now growing so fast after we exposed them to the world. Customers all over the country now purchase items from their online shop, and pay via mobile money, online banking or card services. [/orane_vc_features_small_image][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][orane_vc_features_bgimage title="Wynton House of Music Management system and Portal" feature1l="Admit music students" icon1l="youtube-square" feature2l="Match tutors and available rooms to students" icon2l="youtube-square" feature3l="Create Lessons schedule" icon3l="youtube-square" feature4l="Update the schedule as the parameters change" icon4l="youtube-square" feature1r="Every tutor and student can view schedules relevant to them" icon1r="youtube-square" feature2r="Apply for rescheduling" icon2r="youtube-square" feature3r="Accounting module" icon3r="youtube-square" feature4r="Generate reports and alerts" icon4r="youtube-square" image="95"]Wynton school of music is now digitalised, management simplified, and above all, smooth flow of information between the school and their students, and across all departments.[/orane_vc_features_bgimage][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" type="container"][vc_column][vc_text_separator title="" border_width="3"][vc_gmaps link="#E-8_" title="Located at Mamlaka road, Nairobi Kenya"][contact-form-7 id="4" title="Contact Us"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-26 13:53:54', '2016-07-26 13:53:54', '', 7, 'http://localhost:8084/johnMainaSite/2016/07/26/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
